  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 375°f (190°c).",
    "slice baguette into 1-inch thick rounds.",
    "caramelize onions by cooking 1 large onion, sliced, in 2 tbsp olive oil over low heat for 20-25 minutes.",
    "toast baguette slices by baking in preheated oven for 5-7 minutes.",
    "spread a slice of gouda cheese alternative on each toasted baguette slice.",
    "top each slice with a few leaves of arugula, a slice of yuzu-cured ham, and a spoonful of caramelized onions.",
    "drizzle with mustard and top with pickled red onion.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
